item.description:
Add / edit attribute valueWhile adding or editing an attribute value, the following fields / toggles / parameters are displayed:
Attribute group This drop-down lists all the attributes and is mandatory. In the case of multistore, it lists only the attributes associated with the store(s) selected as context. When the label is hovered, a tooltip is displayed: &ldquo;Choose the attribute group for this value.&rdquo;
Value This field is mandatory and can be translated: When several languages are installed, a drop-down next to the field is displayed.
